d[55381]={r={{n="5x Expulsom or"},{n="or X Spare Parts"},{n="or 40-60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[55382]={r={{n="5x Expulsom or"},{n="or X Spare Parts"},{n="or 40-60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[55383]={r={{n="5x Expulsom or"},{n="or X Spare Parts"},{n="or 40-60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[55463]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Kill 8 Sawblade Clearcutters and use the Living Sap of Nordrassil to regrow 8 stumps. *Fresh-Cut Stumps regrown (8) *Sawblade Clearcutter slain (8) *Living Sap (provided)",de="Look at what they've done to this island, . Nature is nearly extinguished, its death cry falling on the deaf ears of mechagnomes. But I have heard the teeny tiny animals of Mechagon, and bring aid from afar! It won't be easy to restore balance to a land so severely wounded. Nature's scars run deep here. Thankfully, we are not alone. I've brought living sap from Nordrassil, the World Tree of Mount Hyjal. Use it to regrow the forests and speed nature's recovery in this land.",g={n="Mylune",loc="Various"}}
d[55528]={mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate 12 Troggs. * Scrapbone Troggs slain (12)",de="The troggs have been raiding our supplies since we got here, but now that we got some fire power you're going to put a stop to that! Let's teach them troggs to stay away from our stuff!",g={n="Rocket-Chief Fuselage",loc="Area 52, Netherstorm; Rustbolt, Mechagon Island"}}
d[55575]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 100 rare metals using the rare metal collector. * Rare Metal (100) * Rare Metal Collector (provided)",de="The garbage in these trash heaps is full of rare metals: Dalaranium, Suramarite, even Gnomeisium! I've not seen this much easy gold to be had, since they left the vault door open in Boralus! You help me collect some of the metal, and my friend Gao will sell it on the black market. I've got a device that can tear the metal right out of the trash!",g={n="Moxie Lockspinner",x=0.426,y=0.542,loc="Various"}}
d[55658]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},rep="+45 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Discover a clue about the island's history. * Discover a clue",de="Before King Mechagon claimed this island, someone else lived here. Buried beneath this filth and garbage is the history of a forgotten people. With your help, we shall learn about these previous inhabitants. Sir Finley has marked a location where he's seen unusual artifacts. Meet him there and see if you can discover any clues.",g={n="Elise Starseeker",x=0.704,y=0.312,loc="Various"}}
d[55672]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="12 Tortollan Relics collected. * Tortollan Relics (12)",de="The text on this parchment appears to be Tortollan. Is it possible that Tortollans once resided on this island? We need to act quickly, before the creatures in this area destroy anymore evidence. Search the area for any signs of Tortollan relics.",g={n="Sir Finley Mrrgglton",x=0.3805,y=0.4629,loc="Various"}}
d[55688]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="10 Ancient Runestones collected. * Runestone Fragments (10)",de="This runestone could be of Vrykul origins. Is it possible that Vrykul once visited this island? Where there's one runestone, there's usually more. The roots of lashers are drawn to the magic of runestones. If there are more buried here, the Lasher roots maybe wrapped around them! Clear these lashers and see if any have runestones tangled in their roots.",g={n="Sir Finley Mrrgglton",x=0.3805,y=0.4629,loc="Various"}}
d[55695]={mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 8 Golden Cogpaste. * Golden Cogpaste (8)",de="Once every week, Mechagon expels a lot of excess oils through the outflow. That's why the place is a toxic mess! Today they expelled a batch of Golden Cogpaste. The stuff is amazing! I make air fresheners out of it. Make's any mount smell like it's brand new! Check all the pipes in the outflow, and see if you can collect some of this paste.",g={n="Cork Stuttguard",loc="Bondo's Yard, Mechagon Island"}}
d[55717]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Leona Mistcaller, Dunkin Crackjaw, and Adalin Halfheight rescued. * Leaona Mistcaller rescued * Dunkin Crackjaw rescued * Adalin Halfheight rescued",de="That card you found was a Huolon! I think that card belonged to Adalin Halfheight, one of our junior explorer league members. If he dropped it, he and our other junior members maybe in trouble! We need to find Leona Mistcaller, Dunkin Crackjaw, and Adalin Halfheight immediately!",g={n="Sir Finley Mrrgglton",x=0.3805,y=0.4629,loc="Various"}}
d[55718]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},rep="+45 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Deliver the ring to Elise Starseeker. * Night Elf Ring",g={n="Night Elf Ring"}}
d[55743]={r={{n="Recycling Requisition"},{n="Strange Recycling Requisition"}},mo=468000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 1 Bundle of Recyclable Parts * Bundle of Recyclable Parts",g={n="Recyclerizer DX-82"}}
d[55765]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Exterminate 20 motospiders. * Motospiders exterminated (20)",de="You got a problem with mechanical bugs, so the Roughriders are here to sort this mess out! In my experience, this big of an outbreak must have some sort of queen bug behind it all. We gonna go in, kill a lot of bugs till we find the leader of 'em all. Horde or Alliance don't matter, you're with the Roughriders today. Let's kill some bugs!",g={n="Razak Ironsides",x=0.606,y=0.686,loc="Various"}}
d[55813]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="12 Rustwing Ravens slain. * Rustwing Raven's slain (12) *Pedram's Marker Pistol (provided)",de="This conspiracy of ravens is preying on citizens of Rustbolt, it's unacceptable! Prince Erazmin has asked me to reduce their numbers, but I could really use your help. Can you help me kill some of them? Use my marker gun if you need it. I'll blast the ones you mark, and help bring them down.",g={n="Pedram Mechanotrax",loc="Mechagon Island"}}
d[55816]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Scan 10 Clockwork Giants. * Speak with Chromie * Memory Banks Scanned (10) * Robotic-Memory Recorder (provided)",de="In my travels of the many possible futures, I discovered another place much like Rustbolt, but different. In this other time and place, very little is alive, everything is machines. You must travel to this other place. You will scan the memory banks of the Clockwork Giants you find there. Then we will use that data to ensure that our Rustbolt never become's, the other place.",g={n="Chromie",x=0.394,y=0.668,loc="Various"}}
d[55880]={r={{n="Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Use the NRG-100 to charge 6 energy cells. * NRG-100 equipped * Energy Cells Charged (6) * NRG-100 (provided)",de="Welcome back, dear test subject. Today's experiment is... ...My pet project, the NRG-100! I am quite pleased with the potential improvements I've made to efficiency, potency, and destructivity. And the only thing I had to sacrifice was stability! When you're ready to proceed, strap on the NRG-100.",g={n="Pristy Quickcharge",x=0.484,y=0.788,loc="Various"}}
d[55885]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Rescue Trooper Levy, Katrin, and Bybee. * Trooper Bybee rescued * Trooper Levy rescued * Trooper Katrin rescued",de="Some of our Roughrider's are missing, I tried to find them, but got pinned down here by the bugs! I could really use your help, . See if you can save my missing troopers.",g={n="Rico Bugsnapper",loc="Mechagon Island"}}
d[55905]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Free 6 captured Mechagnomes and catch them before they hit the ground. * Mechagnomes caught safely (6) * Clobberbottom's Boomer (provided)",de="We got actual ABDUCTIONS happenin' here, ! Honest to gold, flying robots are swoopin' into town and snatchin' up people like it's closin' time at Gallywix's buffet! Lucky for the Rustbolt Resistance, Gazlowe called in me and my explosives to save the day. You wanna pitch in? Take one of my rocket launchers and blast those containment crates outta the sky. Whatever they've got trapped inside will come tumblin' down real fast, so you gotta run underneath and catch 'em.",g={n="Penny Clobberbottom",loc="Beastwatch, Gorgrond"}}
d[55994]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover 12 containers of Stolen Oil. * Stolen Oil (12)",de="These troggs watch everything we do. They see us pouring oil into various machines, so now they're stealing the oil and drinking it. I think they believe it's going to turn them into machines! We need that oil back, before they drink it all!",g={n="Koupal Oilshins",loc="Scrapbone Den, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56042]={r={{n="Blingtron 7000 Gift Package"}},g={n="Blingtron 7000"}}
d[56049]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+45 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover Adalin's Hearthstone Cards. * Adalin's Cards",de="That ooze seems really hungry! He ate my backpack, compass, pickaxe and my hearthstone cards. Get my cards back!",g={n="Adalin Halfheight",loc="Mechagon Island"}}
d[56053]={r={{n="Spare Parts x20"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Kill Bondo Bigblock. * Bondo Bigblock slain",de="Those of us with enough mechanization survived, but it didn't matter. Bondo Bigblock sold us out. In exchange for full mechanization, he built giant bots and attacked Rustbolt. He will continue to act against us, till those few of us left are dead. We must remove this threat immediately. (Bondo Biglock: Fully mechanized and loyal to King Mechagon.)",g={n="Izira Gearsworn",loc="Rustbolt, Mechagon Island; Operation: Mechagon"}}
d[56082]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="15 attacking bots slain. * Attacking Bots destroyed (15)",de="Those bots have been attacking us from the moment we landed. We've got to hold this beach! My expedition guards could use your help . Lend a hand, destroy bots on the beach and in the nearby woodlands.",g={n="Corey Clockbonk",loc="Overspark Expedition Camp, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56083]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="15 attacking bots slain. *Attacking bots slain (15)",de="Those rampaging bots ain't lettin' up! We're payin' good money for the best and brightest goblins on the planet, and I ain't gonna let some malfunctionin' machinery take 'em outta the shift schedule. This is textbook unsafe working conditions, and the Greasemonkey Union reps are givin' me an earful for it. Protect the workers!",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[56142]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},mo=234000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="20 Pristine Hound Bolts, 4 Steel Tibia XS, and 2 Machined Heel Nut. * Pristine Hound Bolts (20) * Leg Strut XS (4) * Sentry Heel Nut (2)",de="Izira Gearsworn is still alive, she is Rustbolt's strongest fighter, but her legs are broken. If we're going to survive I need parts to repair and upgrade her. There are machines all over with parts we can salvage. With some perseverance we should be able to fix Izira's legs. Help me obtain the following parts.",g={n="Christy Punchcog",loc="Rustbolt, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56184]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=234000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover DeMeza's father's Sword, Clothing and Bones. * Father's Sword * Father's Clothes * Father's Bones * Ride Macaw to Western Spray (Optional)",de="I finally found it! This is the resting place of my father, after his crew mutinied and left him here to die. I've scouted the island, and found the locations of three chests that contain mementoes of my father. Do this for me and my family. Recover my father's sword, clothing, and bones from the three chests I've marked.",g={n="Dread Captain DeMeza",x=0.4,y=0.726,loc="Various"}}
d[56301]={mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover the Murloc Treasure Bag. * Chief Curglrrmrgur slain * Murloc Treasure * Chief's Key",de="I've heard lot's of stories about dead fathers, mothers, and family treasures. Don't believe any of it. We're all here to get any pirate gold, before these mecha-fools get it first! If there's gold to be had here, it's in that fat chest the murlocs are guarding. Kill their chief, empty out the chest, and we'll split it fifty-fifty, since I'm telling ya about it. (Chief Curglrrmrgur: A notorious collector of lost pirates gold.)",g={n="Short John Mithril",loc="Gurubashi Arena, Cape of Stranglethorn"}}
d[56306]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover 75 Family Jewels * Family Jewelry (75)",de="Darn pirates stole my jewels... err, I mean my sister's... uh, mom's jewelry. Yeah, that's the story! Point is, they stole it, and it's all out there strewn around in the mud, and treasure chests. Maybe on a few of the robots and murlocs. My mom's not greedy, she just wants a few of the necklaces with gold and lots of diamonds. I'd pay ya for those.",g={n="Sneaky Pete",x=0.462,y=0.93,loc="Various"}}
d[56322]={r={{n="10x Brewfest Prize Token"}},mo=234000,o="Talk to Brewmaster Tsing in the Brewfest grounds.",g={n="Contained Alemental"}}
d[56326]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Rescue 8 injured mechagnomes. * Injured Mechagnomes rescued (8)",de="A conspiracy of ravens is preying on citizens of Rustbolt! It's most unacceptable! Prince Erazmin has asked me to rescue as many citizens as I can, but I could use your help. I've tracked the ravens to this hill. We blast the ravens out of the sky, and you rescue the mechagnomes. Use my marker gun if you need help bringing the ravens down.",g={n="Pedram Mechanotrax",loc="Mechagon Island"}}
d[56327]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="12 Re-animated bots delivered to Bolten Springspark. * Re-animated Bots delivered to Bolten Springspark (12) * Bot Re-Energizer obtained from Bolten Springspark",de="Chopping up bots is my business. Any bots you bring to my scrapper will be broken up into useful parts. It's a win for both of us! Use the Bot-Energizer to bring me dead bots, and we'll break them into spare parts.",g={n="Bolten Springspark",loc="Bondo's Yard, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56334]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Whirling Zap-O-Matic slain *Whirling Zap-O-Matic slain",de="It's loose up there! I told them not to do it, but they didn't listen. Now it's gone out of control and killed everyone up there. It's an experimental Whirlbot, they never should have built it! You need to stop it before it comes down here looking for more victims! Kill the Whirling Zap-O-Matic.",g={n="Tyler Swaptech",loc="Mechagon Island"}}
d[56341]={r={{n="10x Brewfest Prize Token"}},mo=234000,o="Talk to Verra Fireblood in the Brewfest grounds.",g={n="Direbrew Cog"}}
d[56355]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate 10 Upgraded, Anodized, or Corroded Sentry wherever you find them. * Mechagon Sentry slain (10)",de="A weapon like this could really turn the tide against King Mechagons Troops. Let's go see how their gear matches up against our new toy. Take out King Mechagon's Sentries wherever you can find them",g={n="Rocket-Chief Fuselage",loc="Area 52, Netherstorm; Rustbolt, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56361]={r={{n="Expulsom"},{n="Spare Parts"},{n="40x - 60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Gila Crosswires",x=0.776,y=0.406,loc="Various"}}
d[56362]={r={{n="5x Expulsom or"},{n="or X Spare Parts"},{n="or 40-60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[56363]={mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Gila Crosswires",x=0.776,y=0.406,loc="Various"}}
d[56364]={r={{n="5x Expulsom or"},{n="or X Spare Parts"},{n="or 40-60x War Resources"}},mo=2000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",g={n="Skaggit",x=0.45,y=0.898,loc="Various"}}
d[56365]={r={{n="Spare Parts x40"}},mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Deliver the Visual Holo Sphere to Izira Geasworn in Rustbolt. * Visual Holo Sphere obtained from Armored Vaultbot * Craft an from Pascal-K1N6. (optional)",de="You exist here due to a time anomaly, but you must return to your own time and help us there. The Visual Holo Sphere from the Vaultbot nearby contains the data necessary to defeat King Mechagon before he can use the Mechoriginator. Deliver the Visual Holo Sphere to me in your reality. With luck I will be able to rewind history and prevent this existence from ever happening.",g={n="Izira Gearsworn",loc="Rustbolt, Mechagon Island; Operation: Mechagon"}}
d[56372]={r={{n="10x Brewfest Prize Token"}},mo=234000,o="Talk to Arcti in the Brewfest grounds.",g={n="Hozen Totem"}}
d[56373]={mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Kill the Rolly Gulper and catch 3 Bubble-eyed Rolly. * Rolly Gulper slain * Bubble-eyed Rolly (3)",de="The Bubble-eyed Rolly used to be plentiful in the nearby pond. Last week they all started to vanish! A large water elemental has been swallowing all the fish! They are still alive, just swimming around inside the elemental now. I need you to kill that elemental, and catch three Bubbly-eyed Rolly so I can examine their condition.",g={n="Danielle Anglers",loc="Toothy Shallows, Mechagon Island; Wild Coast, Waking Shores"}}
d[56380]={mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Destroy the Aerial Patroller XZ-2 * Aerial Patroller XZ-2 slain",de="One of King Mechagon's older Aerial units is having mechanical problems and is grounded nearby. They're trying to get it repaired, so we need to act fast while it's vulnerable. Destroy the Aerial Patroller XZ-2 before they can get it repaired.",g={n="Brian Pitchspark",loc="Fleeting Forest, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56402]={r={{n="325x Coalescing Visions"},{n="and random War Resources"},{n="Azerite (resource)"},{n="or Money"}},mo=234000,rep="+125 Uldum Accord",o="Collect 6 Wastewander Coins. * Wastewander Coin (6)",de="It may be too late for some of our fallen brothers and sisters, but it is not too late to give solace to their families. Every Wastewander carries with them a unique coin, signifying their status as a member of our group. If you find any of these coins, please bring them to me and I will make sure they are properly returned to their next of kin.",g={n="Outrider Lashan",loc="Orsis, Uldum"}}
d[56405]={r={{n="Cogfrenzy's Construction Toolkit"},{n="Spare Parts x40"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Help build construction projects. *Contribute to construction projects",de="You Rustbolt resisters inspire me. Tinkering, building, exploring. Letting your imagination run wild and then chasing after it, wherever it leads, with reckless abandon! I miss those days. I hope, someday, my conscience will allow me to stay on the surface with you all permanently... Before I return to Mechagon, we must build something incredible. Waren and I have identified a large number of extra construction projects sites for today. Build with boldness!",g={n="Walton Cogfrenzy",x=0.734,y=0.336,loc="Various"}}
d[56410]={r={{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=468000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Recover Corrupted Disc Fragment * Corrupted Data Disc * Speak with R33-DR * Data Anomaly destroyed",de="King Mechagon unit in possession of Norgannon disk. Data is corrupted, possession of such data is dangerous. Please aid in the recover of Corrupted Disk Fragments that have been discarded via Mechagon waste systems. Deliver recovered Corrupted Disc Fragment to Data Analyzer R33-DR for purging.",g={n="Archivist Bitbyte",x=0.72,y=0.365,loc="Rustbolt, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56434]={r={{n="40x Spare Parts"}},mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate Junkbrat and Roadtrogg. * Junkbrat slain * Roadtrogg slain * Suggested players: 3",de="Responsible for a spree of mayhem and chaos throughout the Heaps, resulting in the theft of energy cells, spare parts, and the consumption of Improbable Mechano-Chicken Wings without payment. Special caution around Roadtrogg, who has demonstrated a violent attitude towards living things. Elimination of these two felons is of the highest priority. (Junkbrat and Roadtrogg: Capable of mayhem anywhere at anytime.)",g={n="Wanted: Junkbrat and Roadtrogg"}}
d[56469]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},rep="+45 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Deliver the old pirate hat to Reno Jackson. * Old Pirate Hat",g={n="Old Pirate Hat"}}
d[56471]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=468000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Destroy Pummeller Red, Pummeller Orange, and Pummeller Grey * Pummeller Grey slain * Pummeller Red slain * Pummeller Orange slain",de="This land is already a monumental disaster, but it could get worse! The Venture Company is here, and will exploit this land for every ounce of profit they can make. We must make their venture here unprofitable, so they will leave. Destroy the three expensive security units with them, and they may leave for more profitable ventures.",g={n="Maokka",loc="Jeweled Coast, Stormsong Valley; Rustbolt, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56493]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate 12 Venture Co. employees * Tech Scavenger slain (12)",de="Maokka has such a gentle heart. He is so good with the little ones, always playing games and telling stories. We do however really dislike these Venture Co. individuals, so I suggest a more direct approach. Try killing them all.",g={n="Scrollsage Nola",x=0.72,y=0.372,loc="Various"}}
d[56501]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate 5 Venture Co. Transports * Venture Co. Transport destroyed (5) * BOOM-TASTIC 3000 (provided)",g={n="Venture Co. Rocket Box"}}
d[56508]={r={{n="Spare Parts"}},mo=234000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 20 Useful Bits and Pieces * Useful Bits and Pieces (20)",g={n=":Useful Bits and Pieces"}}
d[56523]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 20 Mechanical Giblets and repair the OOX-Bomber/MG. * Mechanical Giblets (20) * OOX-Bomber/MG repaired",de="If you've spent any time with that arrogant nitwit, Overspark, you know why I'm here. To silence his boasting and finally prove that my inventions are better! I've released countless mechanical chickens across this island to analyze the technology here, adopt it, and evolve their own circuitry. One of them will become my ultimate battle chicken! But those idiot troggs think my chickens are edible and keep bashing them. Protect them, so my techno-evolutionary experiment can run its course.",g={n="Oglethorpe Obnoticus",x=0.43,y=0.72,loc="Various"}}
d[56532]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},mo=468000,rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Eliminate the 5 Reinforced Sparkweave Eggs * Norbit Controls activated * Motospiders destroyed (40) * Reinforced Sparkweave Eggs destroyed with Scrap Bomb (5)",de="These motospiders continue to multiply unchecked. If we don't slow them down they'll overrun Rustbolt soon. I've modified Norbit here with adequate firepower to take the spiders head on! Would you pilot Norbit and destroy the Reinforced Sparkweave Eggs?",g={n="Dashman Hammerall",loc="Sparkweaver Point, Mechagon Island"}}
d[56550]={mo=234000,o="Burn 10 Egg-bearing corpses. * Egg-bearing Corpses burned (10) *Torch (Uldum) (provided)",de="Our friends continue to fall as these terrible insects pour of their nests and attack our camps. It's a terrible job to ask of anyone, but we have to dispose of the corpses as quickly as possible. We can't allow our dead to be used as fertilizer for growing their disgusting eggs.",g={n="Tracker Samara",loc="Ankhaten Harbor, Uldum"}}
d[56552]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Brawl with Grumbol Grimhammer's forces on Mechagon. * Grumbol's Hammers defeated",de="Gazlowe hired you for protection too? I guess it's true that he only hires the best, eh? Ha! Pay's great, but the rules are dung: no fightin' in town, no exceptions. Bah! That tiny tender prince won't give us his tech unless he thinks we're good little angels... Ha! But Gazlowe didn't say nothin' about fightin' outside of town. I got my own squad on the outskirts, ready to brawl with Grumbol's guzzlers if they show their bearded faces. You want in?",g={n="Usha Eyegouge",x=0.6038,y=0.2913,loc="Various"}}
d[56557]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Slay 5 Alliance players in Mechagon. *Alliance players slain",de="There are only two things more fun than fighting, and the first is talking trash! That boar-beard runt over there's been a thorn in my backside since Alterac... Can't seem to shake him. We got a bet going about who's the best fighter on the island. You want to help me win this wager?",g={n="Usha Eyegouge",x=0.6038,y=0.2913,loc="Various"}}
d[56558]={r={{n="Spare Parts"},{n="Energy Cell"},{n="Empty Energy Cell"}},rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Brawl with Usha Eyegouge's forces on Mechagon. *Usha's Eyegougers defeated",de="*buuuurrp* Arrrright, listen 'ere. We got ourselves a bit o' a predicament. Besides this dump's ale tastin' like oil, that pigheaded Usha here been sayin' some unfortunate stuff about our troops. Unfortunate FOR HER, 'cuz now *uuuuurp* gonna needya ta rough up any Horde swine ya end up runnin' into out there. Loosely speakin' we ain't supposed to be brawlin' out 'ere, so this ain't a formal order or nothin'...",g={n="Grumbol Grimhammer",x=0.4181,y=0.4258,loc="Various"}}
d[56559]={r={{n="Spare Parts x40"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Slay 5 Horde players in Mechagon. *Horde players slain",de="'Ey, , I could be usin' yer talents fer a little bet I got goin' on with Usha. I'm wagerin' you can beat up five 'o her pals around the island before her dog can beat up five o' ours. Ye up fer it me ? 'O course ya are, ahahaha!",g={n="Grumbol Grimhammer",x=0.4181,y=0.4258,loc="Various"}}
d[56572]={r={{n="Azeroth Mini: Starter Pack"},{n="Spare Parts x40"}},mo=234000,rep="+150 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Quasi-Facet scan creatures in Mechagon * Scan creatures in Mechagon * Quasi-Faceted Scanner (provided)",de="I must share the wonders of this place with all of Azeroth in a way that will entertain young and old alike. I will use the technology here to create a new line of toys unlike anything seen before! My Quasi-Faceted scanner can help construct perfect replicas of things here on the island. I just need a helpful individual such as yourself to scan a few things around this area.",g={n="Jepetto Joybuzz",x=0.44,y=0.45,loc="Various"}}
d[56573]={r={{n="Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 15 Salvaged Mechagnome Appendages. * Salvaged Mechagnome Appendage (15)",de="First, let me say that you will ALWAYS be our favorite test subject. But our experiments require far more sacrifice than a single test subject can offer. And, from time to time, some of those test subjects require new limbs. My dear brother and I have a nascent concept for expanding the average lifespan of mechanical appendages. But we've run out of components to experiment on. Salvage some appendages from the heap outside town so we can continue our experiments.",g={n="Pristy Quickcharge",x=0.484,y=0.788,loc="Various"}}
d[56621]={r={{n="Energy Cell"}},rep="+75 Rustbolt Resistance",o="Collect 15 discarded technologies from techno-animated sludge. * Activate :Spark-7143 in The Outflow * Discarded Technology (15) * Spark-7143 (provided)",de="When I say that power is life, I'm not speaking figuratively, my dear test subject. Properly harnessed, power can create life itself--or at least a close enough facsimile for our purposes. There is a massive reserve of discarded technology lurking deep in the mucky depths of the Outflow. As usual, Mechagon's trash is our treasure. I've finally perfected my device that will animate the sludge to bring that technology up to the surface for you. All you have to do is pop 'em and grab the tech!",g={n="Flip Quickcharge",x=0.484,y=0.788,loc="Various"}}
